- Added Dark Theme Support
- Added Perplexity Search Support (requires API key)
- Improved loading of files to Ollama using Chunking and summarization - files are split into chunk, summarized and then submitted to the LLM
- Added a settings section for Perplexity API key and also to control file chunking sizes
- Added "Don't summarize" checkbox for when you don't want attached files to be summarized, such as when its a code file.
- Added support for more different files types - now supports .txt, .pdf, .html, .json, .py, .csv
- Fixed a race condition with IndexedDB
- Fixed a race condition with image submittal
- Added an image icon in the title
